data.text:
List of notable businesses founded in San Francisco, listed alphabetically with corporate logos when available. This list includes some of the largest, most profitable companies that were founded in San Francisco. The famous San Francisco companies and corporations on this list include both public and private corporations. You can find information about the popular companies on this list, such as what industry they're part of. When available you can click on the successful San Francisco company's names to find out even more about them.

The list you're viewing is made up of items like Hewlett-Packard and Levi Strauss & Co..

This list answers the questions, "What companies were founded in San Francisco?" and "What are the biggest San Francisco companies?"

If you're a San Francisco native then this list of the biggest San Francisco companies will make you proud. This list is also an excellent resource if you're doing research on reputable businesses from San Francisco.
